Searching.description:
Excited to share my edit of On June's 'The Devil's Tears' with you!

Discovered the 17 year old @onjune when his track was trending in the Deep House playlist on Soundcloud. He worked together with Australian singer Tesity to make an amazing version of the @angusandjuliastone original.
Honored to make an edit of this track.
Enjoy :)

Out now on all portals! samfeldt.lnk.to/thedevilstears
Searching.title: The Devil's Tears
